Such a talented family Attaullah Essakhelvi also known as "LaLa" is Punjabi,Seriaki and urdu classic singer.His Son Sanwal Essakhelvi is singer,designer and composer.
while his daughter Laraib khan atta is first Pakistani and youngest professional VFX artist in Hollywood ,she worked as a visual effects artist for many Hollywood films including X-Men; Days of Future Past, Godzilla, Gravity, The Chronicles of Narnia The Voyage of the Dawn Trader and Prince Caspian, 10,000 BC and Johnny Depp’s Sweeney Todd and Mission Impossible Fallout.
